genresAdvancedInfo.name: png pop
genresAdvancedInfo.description: A genre of popular music originating from Papua New Guinea, characterized by its upbeat rhythms, catchy melodies, and use of traditional instruments and vocal styles. It often incorporates elements of reggae, hip-hop, and electronic music, and has gained popularity both domestically and internationally.
